parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, injuries, or strandings.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle loses power
the transmission fails to engage or disengage
the vehicle is stuck in gear
the transmission shudders or vibrates
the vehicle stalls
the transmission warning light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sliding door and its hinges can cause the door to fall off or become stuck, leading to accidents, injuries, or strandings.
symptoms: The sliding door falls off or becomes stuck
the door hinges break or rust
the door is hard to open or close
the door comes off track
the door flies open while driving
the door latch jams
and the door won't shut properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the liftgate support bracket can cause the liftgate to fall down, leading to accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The liftgate falls down
the liftgate support bracket breaks
the hydraulic lift arm fails
the liftgate won't stay open
the liftgate slams shut
and the liftgate glass shatters.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Paint Peeling and Clear Coat Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling of the paint and clear coat can cause the paint to flake off, leading to rust and corrosion, which can compromise the vehicle's structural integrity.
symptoms: The paint peels off
the clear coat fails
the paint flakes off
and the surface rusts or corrodes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the vehicle to skid or lose braking ability, leading to accidents or near-accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle skids or loses braking ability when braking

especially on snow-covered or slushy roads; the brake pedal feels soft or spongy; the brake pedal goes to the floor without warning; grinding noises in the brakes; the ABS warning light comes on; the brake pedal becomes stiff and the vehicle does not stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents or near-accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor without warning; grinding noises in the brakes; the brake pedal feels soft or spongy; the brake pedal becomes stiff and the vehicle does not stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Cruise Control and Brake System Interaction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The interaction between the cruise control and brake system can cause the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents or near-accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates unexpectedly when the cruise control is engaged and the brakes are applied; the vehicle continues to speed even after the brakes are released.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake noise and fading can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents or near-accidents.
symptoms: Brake noise followed by brake fading; burning odor when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Wheel Sensor Failure for ABS System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wheel sensor can cause the ABS system to malfunction, leading to accidents or near-accidents.
symptoms: The ABS warning light comes on; the wheel sensor fails
causing the ABS system to malfunction.
